article.headline: Charting a pulling-teeth breakout attempt:  S&P 500, Nasdaq challenge record territory
article.body: Technically speaking, the U.S. benchmarks’ bigger-picture backdrop remains comfortably bullish as market rotation persists. Consider that the Nasdaq Composite and S&P 500 have registered nominal record highs this week — tagging previously uncharted territory — though a pulling-teeth breakout attempt remains underway.
